  .use(LanguageDetector)
  .use(initReactI18next)
  .init({

      en: enTranslations,
      uk: ukTranslations,

    fallbackLng: 'en',
    debug: process.env.NODE_ENV === 'development',

      escapeValue: false, // not needed for React
    },
  });
